description:
new sublimation (all over) print top,

these tops are of extremely high quality, they are a slimmer fit so we recommend to size up from your normal size.

*this product may contain white crease lines found near the seams of the shirt especially on the armpit of the shirt and slight fading near collar area these are common things found on sublimation prints due to the sublimation process and are barely noticeable*
